      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MINTER MULWEE (2) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 8th at this track following on from a third place finish (23.35) there the start prior. Has a good record here at this journey. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Has claims if he runs up to expectations. RAMJET (1) gave a start after copping a check in running and missed the frame when a 6 length fifth (22.90) at Maitland in a Grade 5. Safe beginner and drawn well on the inside. Must include in calculations. SUNSHINE RHONDA (8) finished well back at this track last time when a 14 length fifth (23.73) but scored five back at this track (23.08). Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Great chance to atone.",
